frus:attachment.p:
Whereas, The preceding convention was approved by the Senate of the
                            United States of Mexico the tenth day of May of the present year, and
                            ratified by me the fourteenth day of the said month;

Whereas the preceding convention was approved by the senate of the United
                            States of Mexico the 10th day of December, 1886, and ratified by mo the
                            31st day of May of the present year;
